{
  "stem": "15686.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what we had gone through in Germany and what have you, they helped us-- my teacher, at least-- my homeroom teacher helped in every way she could.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She helped me with my French, and she helped me in every other way.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was a good student.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had-- by that time, I was fluent in French and kept up with the others.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I really wasn't any problem.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Some of the other kids had more of a tough time with the French.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I-- I didn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I was lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we had no news at all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We tried through the Red Cross to find out what had happened to them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the only news that we received was that there were 20,000 Jews in Shanghai.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They lived in a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were not being harmed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If we could send food packages, we should, which was a little facetious, because we didn't have enough to eat ourselves.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Food by that time was rationed in France.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And of course, we couldn't send any packages to them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the Red Cross sent some forms.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they said, well, you can fill out this form.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And on the bottom, there are three lines for a personal message.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And maybe we can get this through, and maybe not.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We can't promise, but you can try.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we did that, but it didn't help.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we are now sort of at the end of spring of 1940.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in 1940, the German army went on the offensive and invaded France.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It did not take very long after Paris fell.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The next morning-- we were still in Orsay-- we heard the noise of marching outside.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we looked outside, very early in the morning, 5 o'clock, and they were French soldiers retreating.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
